William Forrest (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Forrest_(actor) 0 William Forrest (October 10, 1902 – January 26, 1989) was an American theatre, film, and television actor. He appeared in more than 250 films between 1939 and 1977. He was born in Cambridge, Massachusetts and died in Santa Monica, California from heart failure.
